Metadata: University of California Sea Grant Extension Program

Tidelines will be published quarterly as a local newsletter dealing with practical problems in the areas of Commercial and sport fisheries; Seafood processing, aquaculture, marine education and youth programs, marine research, waterfront management, boating industry, marine transportation, environmental policy, and coastal engineering. Cover topics include: Trying a new way to cut pollution and costs, Boating nonpoint source pollution - who and what?
